{"tid":1714535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大如果守唔住，就會變仰光大學","createTime":"2019-11-13T01:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T08:56:54.000Z","uid":144626,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ae92315146e2168d56fffd03a848c9bfd3115f5","tid":1714535,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:51:31.000Z","msg":"仰光大學比中大、港大同新加坡國立大學更早發跡<br />\n以前係遠東殖民地頂尖大學之一<br />\n佢嘅醫學院更加同港大齊名<br />\n大家見到緬甸大學畢業嘅醫生多數都係出自呢間野<br />\n<br />\n近代出唔少影響緬甸嘅大人物，如昂山將軍、奈溫等等<br />\n<br />\n係反殖民同反軍政府嘅重要陣地<br />\n但係，軍政府上台之後，多次示威活動後被軍政府攻入<br />\n死傷無數，8888民主運動之後<br />\n更加令到仰光大學慘遭拆骨<br />\n成為一間間小型學院，到近年先至重新收生<br />\n但呢間百年老校已慘遭沒落<br />\n拆骨目的，在於防止反政府思想再次傳播同埋分散學生<br />\n因為各校大多都相當分散，可以逐一攻破<br />\n<br />\n所以，如果守唔住中大，學生安全不保不再話下<br />\n當年由民國學者建立嘅基業，將毀於一旦<br />\n<br />\n頂住啊中大！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02e8e4d13f0a1eb6111085401ad2756e2a64adc","tid":1714535,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:51:55.000Z","msg":"11.14 曙光行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/evpMOT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/evpMOT</a><br />\n<br />\n再接再厲"},{"pid":"f78d09744db241ecd6cbebccc7906de906a2a472","tid":1714535,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3d774b752734e2daa09ef66fab94c9bfb93880","tid":1714535,"uid":119864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:57:43.000Z","msg":"錢穆間大學俾隻臭雞777搞成咁"},{"pid":"253f0476962addcafd8662f99201eb7d693a7431","tid":1714535,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd3d774b752734e2daa09ef66fab94c9bfb93880","tid":1714535,"uid":119864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2